{"type": "article", "id": 58307, "title": "金属框架与乳胶床垫的组合，可在床和沙发之间任意切换｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-11-14T23:11:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 54239, "name": "Artish Studio"}, {"id": 8331, "name": "吱音"}, {"id": 54240, "name": "Rowena Edwards"}, {"id": 54241, "name": "Emma Sicher"}, {"id": 54242, "name": "Pan Biwei"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 134, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181114190652XN2aOb13EldZIU8V.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>SHO by Pan Biwei</h3><p>沙发椅 SHO 是今年红点设计概念奖的获得者，出自设计师 Pan Biwei 之手。它由框架和床垫组成，几秒钟之内就可以从沙发转换成沙发床。金属框架与乳胶床垫可以轻松变换出床、椅子和躺椅三种状态。</p><p>直立位置非常适合坐着和阅读。只需松开扣环并展开床垫，就可以创造一个合适的躺椅，在这里可以伸展双腿，放松身心，同时享受背部支撑。尤其小巧的体积可折叠的功能，是都市人小空间的一种选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114190732XTBZ4igvrW5ebnjD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.823810\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114190734krhxRKSI0W86cL1t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114190735bEygXL4j1DVOl2pr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018111419073648eqth2fQLJsEHo9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.834286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114190736bol23QDeU5fENX0r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/11/13/the-cushion-tamer/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>答案小酒柜 by 吱音</h3><p>家居设计品牌吱音推出新品“答案小酒柜”。喜酒之人都喜欢珍藏精酿，让不同高度的酒瓶都能找到适合安放的柜子，不仅满足收藏需求，亦可升华情趣。即使是不常沾酒的人，难免也要存上几瓶红酒、香槟，在节假日亲友聚餐时，从容应对即兴而饮。</p><p>灵活可变的模块化组合，周到地解决不同收纳需求，总能刚刚好成为你最想要的那个“答案”。高高的红酒瓶和玻璃高脚杯，在用过之后也能拥有一处稳妥又方便的专属空间。</p><p>答案小酒柜顶层厚度约 15 毫米，用户可以选择无痕免钉的高脚杯架配合使用，节约更多空间。上层的小平台也可变身为调酒桌。低矮的杯子、餐具都可以分类归纳。另有一个可调节搁板，方便摆放不同高度的物品，同时也可作实用储物的餐边柜。售价 3999 元起，<a href=\"https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.5-b-s.w4011-16671124525.119.4bf61abbRjfMsL&amp;id=581333770201&amp;rn=43641f1441926bcfc80415f3b3e2b400&amp;abbucket=11&amp;sku_properties=13744110:37462894\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114190814NCGAnqOPiIHXoj9z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.864000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114190816pbYBNfcgeQldL9uV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.080000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114190817Z2lD510poPNey7tH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.229333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114190817ts6leBo13kiHuXYI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.260000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114190818eRqmlEJQvGL1b8jf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114190819FtENgcyjuz6XHRVn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.396000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>From Peel to Peel by Emma Sicher </h3><p>意大利设计师 Emma Sicher 将食物垃圾与细菌、酵母混合在一起，制造了一次性包装，以提供可持续的塑料替代品。</p><p>这个项目名为 Peel to Peel，Emma Sicher 通过发酵微生物纤维素制造环保食品包装和容器，微生物纤维素是一种细菌和酵母的共生培养物，含有水果和蔬菜残羹剩饭。微生物将碎片中的果糖和维生素转化为纯纤维素，直至形成明胶状物质，然后根据所需的厚度将该混合物静置 2 至 4 周，然后加热和干燥。干燥后，它变成半透明的材料片，具有与纸张、塑料和皮革相似的特性。</p><p>设计师还尝试了不同的水果和蔬菜，如苹果、土豆、甜菜根、葡萄果渣和啤酒花，以创造不同颜色和纹理的材料。设计师希望她的有机包装可以替代广泛使用的塑料和纸包装。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114190910CMlbqLGwS5YUcT7v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114190911mcMq4bktofs6UgPn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645516\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114190913sMSk3FG4WBY0v6UL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.916667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114190914o3UE8TgReMv41S2s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.696277\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114190915piCrVNUFueWm5ZtR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664975\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811141909182EdPcf0aGxT1H5Sj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713621\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/11/13/sustainable-food-packaging-emma-sicher-peel/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Interactive Products by Artish Studio</h3><p>Artish Studio 总部位于北卡罗来纳州罗利市，是一家新近推出的设计工作室，意在通过用户可以使用的互动产品重新定义一些常见的产品。</p><p>最近他们发布了第一个系列，特点是可以随时重新配置，包括地板雕塑套件 Stones，磁性墙艺术套件和边桌。</p><p>Stones 套件，包括几何胶合板形状，用户可以通过其互锁槽系统将它们组合在一起，制成各种艺术品。磁性墙艺术套件意味着你的墙壁将成为自我表达的展示空间，该套件配有涂漆钢片，可以随意移动和重新排列。</p><p>边桌有两个版本，Cee和 Zee，每个都是用彩绘折叠钢制成的，内置磁铁，可以拼接成更大的桌面，也可以添加到墙壁套件里组合使用。售价 65 美元起，<a href=\"https://www.artishstudio.com/shop\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114191020k8Qb04hMvDfPRt9A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114191020imZe0sRwOkfuXhnI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114191021XD0lFQOongdt5bZ2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.678906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114191022waOM1lgRXAb2hIpk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114191022F8soDL9x1Ir5hmQz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.766406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114191023ojMi6hZzYlgJ5FKP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114191023k85vVYWJrMumN6gA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114191026kjMdNmVSlrBK5zvu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>ROWND Drinks Cabinet by Rowena Edwards </h3><p>家用收纳、陈列小推车近两年来新作频出，但大多是典型的四轮推车或是双层推车。</p><p>最近，威尔士家具和产品设计师 Rowena Edwards 推出了一款全新的家用推车 ROWND，将柜体嵌入车轮，结构新颖。</p><p>柜体嵌在两个大圆形面板内，圆面板也可以作为轮子使用。两侧都有口袋可容纳额外的物件。橡木柜体搭配明亮的黄色钢制部件组合而成，不仅可以将推车保持在适当位置，而且可以旋转起来作为把手将其拉到另一个位置。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114191108aZAO29SohHT1mbD7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114191108KTOmlh0N3ZcfAyxe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811141911096PCTJYxbtjlvkOaN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114191110Mferx1y8PCzgN0uH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018111419111039ozniGM7RraWFcA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-rownd-drinks-cabinet-takes-bar-carts-to-a-whole-new-level/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114191111JmWincZP1IlCrMtN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}